Feature: Manage ODM Vendor Attributes in Clinical MDR API
    As an API user, I want to manage ODM Vendor Attributes through the Clinical MDR API endpoints.

    Background: Test user must be able to call the Clinical MDR API, and the test data exists
        Given The test user can call the Clinical MDR API

    Scenario: User must be able to get an empty list of ODM vendor attributes
        When the user calls the API endpoint 'concepts/odms/vendor-attributes'
        Then the response must include an empty list of ODM vendor attributes
        And the response status code must be 200
